sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant SeatInv as Seat Inventory Service
    participant Redis as Redis Hold Cache
    participant Rabbit as RabbitMQ DLQ

    SeatInv->>Redis: delete hold:{inventoryId}
    alt delete succeeds
        Redis-->>SeatInv: key removed or already missing
        SeatInv-->>SeatInv: continue normally
    else delete fails
        loop CACHE_RETRY_ATTEMPTS
            SeatInv->>Redis: retry delete with backoff
        end
        alt still failing
            SeatInv->>Rabbit: publish cache_invalidation_failed event
            SeatInv-->>SeatInv: warn operators for manual follow-up
        end
    end
